    </div>

    <p>The gummy supplements on this list target cortisol through the hypothalamic-pituitary-adrenal (HPA) axis — the neuroendocrine cascade that regulates cortisol production. Adaptogens like ashwagandha and rhodiola modulate HPA axis signaling to prevent excessive cortisol release, while ingredients like phosphatidylserine and GABA address the downstream effects of elevated cortisol on the nervous system.</p>

