        <p>An Arctic adaptogen that modulates cortisol through AMPK pathway activation and heat shock protein regulation. A 2012 study in Phytomedicine found rhodiola reduced cortisol response to acute stress by 23%. Best for physical and mental fatigue.</p>
      </div>
